			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">The future supply routes reviewed in this study are based on data gathered from technical reports and environmental impact assessment reports of several lithium mining and processing companies (Lithium Americas Corp., Minera Salar Blanco, Nemaska Lithium Inc., and Keliber Oy) that are at various stages of developing their lithium assets. These are considered future supply routes as they are not yet active but areexpected to be operational in 5–10 years. The lower lithium concentrations at these brine-based sources also reflect the possible future lithium grades of current supply routes from brines, whose lithium concentrations will likely decrease over the years due to extraction</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">本研究审查的未来供应路线是基于从几家锂矿开采和加工公司（Lithium Americas Corp.、Minera Salar Blanco、Nemaska Lithium Inc.和Keliber Oy）的技术报告和环境影响评估报告中收集的数据，这些公司的锂资产正处于不同的开发阶段。这些锂资产正处于不同的开发阶段。预计在 5-10 年内投入运营。这些以卤水为基础的来源的锂浓度较低，也反映了当前供应路线中卤水的未来锂品位。</common:generalComment>
		</dataSetInformation>
